ad86ec987febdbc9bfe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F042117_c50e0f8bd958ad86ec987febdbc9bfe8.jpg&h=79be56ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你個問題同問女人係咪屎忽生仔冇分別"},{"pid":"d723b1453f1951b5025433203082864dd1024dfd","tid":428982,"uid":39700,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T20:56:52.000Z","msg":"會架呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你要小心d<br />\n睇下自己睪丸有冇腫脹<br />\n有腫脹記得睇醫生<br />\n以上情況好大機會<br />\n你自己兩粒精子已經結合左<br />\n胚胎發育緊<br />\n唔理到後期會爆春袋而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於特徵係點睇<br />\n你睇下你春袋有冇一縮一脹既情況<br />\n脹起黎會離身 條條fing <br />\n呢個時候就一定有問題<br />\n<br />\n利申：脹左切左春袋<br />\n<br />\n我有相熟醫生可以平d介紹比你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445fce52a2868a5c89828ce78e547a938b04520b","tid":428982,"uid":3548,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T21:34:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 成班弱鳩智唔明樓主講咩<br />\n<br />\n佢意思係如果張兩個男人既精液溝埋再射落條女個閪到會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27d59f09029d5c5e35f48c1fc96b16814d70ebc","tid":428982,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T21:54:18.000Z","msg":"驗dna"},{"pid":"f0bc2473ba409c11f811a663a1130662af2dd04e","tid":428982,"uid":140523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T21:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母 成班弱鳩智唔明樓主講咩<br />\n<br />\n佢意思係如果張兩個男人既精液溝埋再射落條女個閪到會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一粒卵子只會接受一條精子 就算精液溝埋都唔會有樓主講既混合bb"},{"pid":"4a891b1d967f10c01c89f804d300166981ee71a1","tid":428982,"uid":27305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T21:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母 成班弱鳩智唔明樓主講咩<br />\n<br />\n佢意思係如果張兩個男人既精液溝埋再射落條女個閪到會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似係你